<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>WatchZone - Password Reset</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f2f2f2;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #333; text-align: center;">WatchZone - Password Reset</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; text-align: center;">
            You have requested to reset your password for WatchZone. Please use the following passcode within the next
            10 minutes:
        </p>
        <div
            style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 5px; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px;">
            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">{{ passcode }}</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: #666; text-align: center;">
            This passcode is valid for 10 minutes only.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #666; text-align: center;">
            If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #666; text-align: center;">
            Regards,
        </p>
        <p style="color: #666; text-align: center;">
            WatchZone Team
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>